OL,3,COldham youngsters have their say in
OL,4,Cnational online safety debate
OL,6,FMahdlo Youth Zone's CEO Lucy Lees said
OL,7,F"when we heard about the Government
OL,8,Fdoing a national consultation around
OL,9,Fwhat it is like to grow up in a
OL,10,Fdigital world, it absolutely needed
OL,11,Fyoung people to be part and central to
OL,12,Fthat, otherwise it is central
OL,13,Fgovernment and adults making decisions
OL,14,Ffor them."
OL,16,FYou can find out more about the
OL,17,FGovernment consultation and have your
OL,18,Fsay here
